	<Title>
		Hygiene hypothesis: Early germ exposure prevents asthma?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		According to the hygiene hypothesis, childhood infections may help prevent asthma.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Does childhood exposure to germs help prevent asthma?
	</Question>
